{
  "description": "Headless unit-production mechanic: accrues productionPoints each turn (AI_TURN) and, on an affordable PRODUCE, emits a SPAWN intent for the grid-tactics authority to place a new unit. Owns only productionPoints (+ its spawn counter); never writes units directly.",
